Commander of the Order of Heroes. Hatched
a brilliant strategy for taking advantage of the
new year in order to draw in customers.

Princess of the realm of dead. Is both
delighted and confused by her first New
Year's experience.

A member of the cat clan of laguz. Out enjoying
New Year's treats in unusual garb. Appears in
Fire Emblem: Radiant Dawn.

A carefree kitsune. She's dressed up in a kimono
and ready to join in the New Year's celebrations.
Appears in Fire Emblem Fates.

Siblings who, together, represent Askr's future.
They have come to participate in the celebration
and to make a resolution to keep up their hard
work in the coming year.

(Duo Skills can be used once per map by

be used by units deployed using Pair Up.)

Standard Effect 1: Duel
If unit is 5★ and level 40 and unit's stats total
less than 185, treats unit's stats as 185 in
modes like Arena. (Higher-scoring opponents
will appear. Stat total calculation excludes any
values added by merges and skills.)

Effective against flying foes. At start of turn,
if any foe's Res ≤ unit's Res-3 and that foe is
adjacent to another foe, inflicts Def/Res-5 on
that foe through its next action.

Effective against flying foes. At start of turn,
if any foe's Res ≤ unit's Res-3 and that foe is
adjacent to another foe, inflicts Def/Res-5 on
that foe through its next action.

Accelerates Special trigger (cooldown count-1).
At start of combat, if Special is ready, grants
Atk/Spd/Def/Res+5 during combat and foe
cannot make a follow-up attack.

Grants Spd+3. If unit's Spd > foe's Spd, deals
damage = 70% of difference between stats.
(Maximum bonus of +7 damage. Combos
with Phantom Spd.) If unit's Spd > foe's Spd,
reduces damage from attacks during combat
and from area-of-effect Specials (excluding
Røkkr area-of-effect Specials) by percentage =
difference between stats × 4 (max 40%) .

At start of turn, if unit is adjacent to only beast
or dragon allies or if unit is not adjacent to any
ally, unit transforms (otherwise, unit reverts).
If unit transforms, grants Atk+2, and if unit
initiates combat, inflicts Atk/Def-4 on foe
during combat and foe cannot make a
follow-up attack.

Boosts damage by 50% of unit's Def. Restores
